cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper uses machine learning techniques to analyze videos of human semen samples, which suggests that it belongs to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of deep learning techniques also suggests that it belongs to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The inclusion of participant data suggests that it may also belong to the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. Finally, the use of videos as input data suggests that it may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
